\frac{n!}{x(x+1)\cdots(x+n)} = \binom{n}{0}\frac{1}{x}-\binom{n}{1}\frac{1}{x+1}+\cdots+(-1)^n\binom{n}{n}\frac{1}{x+n}, \quad \text{for } x \not \in \{0,-1,-2,\dots,-n\}
